texts.text: The fun Duck is in the hut.
The Duck really likes to cut paper.
Duck likes to lie in the sun.
Duck likes to swim in the tub.
The red Bug is on the run.
Bug likes to run very fast.
Bug likes to bang on the drum.
Bug likes to chuck small rocks.
Bug likes to play in the brown mud.
Bug looks at the big truck and runs.
Bug sees the white Duck in the tub.
The Bug joins the Duck in the big tub.
Bug likes to have fun with Duck .
Duck and Bug like to hug.
Duck and Bug are two lucky buddies.
Duck and Bug are best buds.
